metadata.description: This (555) piece collection of Art features (5) original pieces of work from Eric Spivak including a dozen unique attributes and each denomination carrying its own intrinsic value. Going beyond the art, each piece is separately part of a larger social experiment where the NFTs individually or combined will be redeemable for a wealth of utilities, unlocking exclusive perks and special benefits at no additional cost. Supporting this project also contributes to my commitments to pushing the boundaries of creativity during this digital renaissance. Lastly, this NFT serves as a key to unlocking parts of the New Friendship Tech ecosystem and will include you in our listing of recognized supporters on the finalized website launching in Q1 of 2023.
